	- Enable flow logs on VPC/subnet/ENI.
	- Analyze logs in CloudWatch/S3.
	- Practice: Deny inbound rule in SG ‚Üí verify drop in flow logs.
	- Interview Qs:
		- How do you debug connectivity using flow logs?
3. Transit Gateway (Concept Only)
	- Hub-and-spoke model to connect multiple VPCs.
	- Difference vs Peering.
	- Interview Qs:
