Week 9 ‚Äî this is where we expand Python for DevOps (automation with JSON/YAML, APIs, boto3, and subprocess).
By the end of this week, you‚Äôll be able to write automation scripts that interact with AWS services, parse logs/configs, and even call shell commands from Python.

üìÖ Week 9: Python for DevOps (Daily Roadmap)
üéØ Goal
- Go beyond basic Python ‚Üí focus on automation, cloud scripting, and DevOps use-cases.
