	- Why private registries? (enterprise apps, sensitive images).
	- docker login, docker tag, docker push.
	- Docker Hub private repos.
	- AWS ECR basics ‚Üí authenticate & push image.
- Practice:
	- Tag & push Flask app image to Docker Hub private repo.
	- Push same image to AWS ECR.
- Mini-Project:
  
   ‚û°Ô∏è docker-registry-demo/ ‚Üí notes + screenshots ‚Üí pushing to Hub & ECR.
- Interview Qs:
	- Why use private registries?
	- How do you authenticate with ECR?

Day 5 ‚Üí Image Security (Trivy)
- Topics:
	- Why scan images? (supply chain attacks, CVEs).
	- Trivy basics ‚Üí scanning local images.
	- Fixing vulnerabilities ‚Üí update base images.
- Practice:
	- Install Trivy ‚Üí scan Flask image.
	- Fix vulnerabilities by using slim base image.
- Mini-Project:
  
   ‚û°Ô∏è docker-security-scan/ ‚Üí repo with Trivy results + fixed Dockerfile.
- Interview Qs:
	- How does Trivy detect vulnerabilities?
	- What‚Äôs the difference between a slim image and full base image?

Day 6 ‚Üí Capstone Project: Multi-Container App with Compose
- Project ‚Üí Build and secure a Docker Compose Stack:
	- Flask app + MySQL database.
	- Persistent volume for MySQL.
	- Custom Docker network.
	- Image scan with Trivy before deployment.
