- Walk me through how Ansible integrates into CI/CD.

‚úÖ End of Week 22 Deliverables
- 5+ repos (Vault, Template, Galaxy, Dynamic Inventory, CI/CD).
- 1 polished repo: ansible-secure-cicd/.
