Week 23 is where we bridge Docker + Ansible, which is something recruiters love to see.
This week you‚Äôll automate container builds, deployments, and configuration management using Ansible + Docker.
By the end of the week, you‚Äôll have a portfolio-ready project: an Ansible-driven Docker App Deployment with automated builds, secrets, and orchestration.

üìÖ Week 23: Docker + Ansible Integration
üéØ Goal
- Automate container image builds with Ansible.
- Use Ansible roles to deploy & manage Dockerized apps.
