üîπ Day 6 ‚Üí Capstone Project: Automated Dockerized App Deployment
Project ‚Üí ‚ÄúDockerized App with Ansible Automation‚Äù
- Flask app + MySQL DB.
- Dockerfile ‚Üí build app image.
- Docker Compose ‚Üí orchestrate services.
