Week 25 is where we take Kubernetes to production-grade level.
So far, you‚Äôve deployed apps in Kubernetes with basics (Pods, Deployments, Services, ConfigMaps, Secrets).
Now we‚Äôll move into production-ready workloads: Helm, StatefulSets, DaemonSets, Jobs/CronJobs, and Observability (logging/monitoring inside K8s).
This week transforms you from ‚Äújust a K8s user‚Äù ‚Üí into someone who can manage real-world Kubernetes workloads like a 2-year experienced DevOps engineer.

üìÖ Week 25: Kubernetes Production Ops (Helm, StatefulSets, DaemonSets, Jobs, Observability)
üéØ Goal
