üîπ Day 4 ‚Üí DaemonSets & Jobs
Topics
- DaemonSets ‚Üí run pods on all (or specific) nodes (e.g., logging, monitoring agents).
- Jobs ‚Üí one-time tasks (batch processing).
- CronJobs ‚Üí scheduled tasks.
Practice
- Deploy Fluent Bit as DaemonSet ‚Üí ship logs.
- Create Job ‚Üí run Python script once.
- Create CronJob ‚Üí run script every 5 min.
