- Alerts with Prometheus Alertmanager.
Practice
- Deploy Prometheus + Grafana via Helm.
- Create Grafana dashboard for pod CPU/memory.
- Deploy Fluent Bit as DaemonSet ‚Üí send logs to stdout/Elasticsearch.
Mini-Project
‚û°Ô∏è k8s-monitoring-logging-demo/ ‚Üí Monitoring + logging stack in K8s.
Interview Qs
