üîπ Day 5 ‚Üí Network Policies & RBAC Hardening
Topics
- Network Policies ‚Üí restrict Pod-to-Pod communication.
- RBAC Hardening:
	- Avoid cluster-admin for apps.
	- Principle of least privilege.
Practice
- Create NetworkPolicy ‚Üí only allow frontend ‚Üí backend traffic.
- Create Role ‚Üí read-only access to Pods in namespace.
Mini-Project
‚û°Ô∏è k8s-secure-network-rbac/ ‚Üí YAML configs for NetPol + RBAC rules.
Interview Qs
- How do Network Policies secure traffic?
- Difference between Role and ClusterRole?

