üîπ Day 1 ‚Üí Image Signing with Cosign (Sigstore)
Topics
- Why image signing? ‚Üí Prevent tampering.
- Sigstore project: Cosign basics.
- Signing Docker images.
- Verifying signatures before deployment.
Practice
- Install Cosign (brew install cosign or binary).
- Build Flask app image ‚Üí sign with Cosign.
- Verify image signature before K8s deployment.
Mini-Project
‚û°Ô∏è cosign-image-signing/ ‚Üí Repo with signed Docker image + verification workflow.
