üîπ Day 2 ‚Üí SBOMs (Software Bill of Materials)
Topics
- What is an SBOM? ‚Üí Inventory of all software dependencies.
- Why it matters (Log4j, open-source vulnerabilities).
- Tools: Syft (generate SBOM), Grype (scan vulnerabilities).
- SBOM in CI/CD pipelines.
Practice
- Generate SBOM for Flask app image with Syft.
- Scan SBOM with Grype ‚Üí detect vulnerabilities.
