	1. Build image.
	2. Generate SBOM.
	3. Sign image.
	4. Verify before deploy.
	5. Enforce policies in K8s.
Practice
- Create Jenkinsfile / GitHub Actions workflow:
	- Build & push ‚Üí sign with Cosign.
	- Generate SBOM with Syft.
	- Run Grype scan.
	- Deploy only if SBOM scan passes.
Mini-Project
‚û°Ô∏è supplychain-cicd-demo/ ‚Üí Pipeline repo with signing, SBOM, and policy enforcement.
