Week 34.
By now you‚Äôve covered Kubernetes, Service Mesh, Cloud Security, Supply Chain Security, and Incident Response.
Now it‚Äôs time to integrate everything into Threat Modeling + Security Automation ‚Üí this is where you start thinking like a DevSecOps Architect, not just an engineer.

üìÖ Week 34: Threat Modeling & Security Automation
üéØ Goal
- Learn how to analyze threats before they happen (STRIDE, DREAD models).
