üîπ Day 1 ‚Üí Threat Modeling Foundations
Topics
- Why threat modeling matters in DevSecOps.
- STRIDE model (Spoofing, Tampering, Repudiation, Information Disclosure, DoS, Elevation of Privilege).
- DREAD model (Damage, Reproducibility, Exploitability, Affected Users, Discoverability).
- Threat modeling tools: Microsoft Threat Modeling Tool, OWASP Threat Dragon.
Practice
- Model a simple 3-tier app (frontend, backend, DB).
- Identify possible threats (SQL injection, privilege escalation, MITM).
