Week 35 is where we bring Observability + Security together ‚Üí also known as SecOps / Security Observability.
By now, you‚Äôve got skills in DevOps, Kubernetes, Cloud Security, and Threat Modeling. This week will make you look like someone who has actually run production systems under attacks and incidents ‚Äî a huge differentiator in interviews.

üìÖ Week 35: Security Observability & Incident Response (SIEM + SOAR)
üéØ Goal
- Learn Security Observability: logs, metrics, traces ‚Üí but with a security focus.
