By now, you‚Äôve nailed container security fundamentals (build, runtime, escape prevention). In Week 38, we expand into Kubernetes Native Security Tools & Advanced Hardening.
This week is about securing the Kubernetes cluster itself at a deeper level using tools like Kyverno, Gatekeeper (OPA), KubeLinter, Kubescape, Aqua/Kube-Bench, and enforcing Pod Security Standards, policies, and compliance frameworks.

üìÖ Week 38: Kubernetes Native Security Tools & Hardening
