üîπ Day 5 ‚Üí Continuous Compliance in CI/CD
Topics
- CI/CD integration with compliance tools.
- Example workflow:
	1. Terraform ‚Üí Checkov scan.
	2. Docker image ‚Üí Trivy scan.
	3. Kubernetes manifests ‚Üí Kyverno policy check.
	4. Reports ‚Üí pushed to Security Hub / ELK.
Practice
- Build GitHub Actions pipeline ‚Üí compliance checks + report artifact.
- Fail pipeline if compliance rules violated.
Mini-Project
‚û°Ô∏è ci-cd-compliance-pipeline/ ‚Üí repo with full compliance pipeline.
Interview Qs
- How do you automate compliance in CI/CD?
- What‚Äôs the difference between Checkov and OPA?

üîπ Day 6 ‚Üí Capstone Project: Compliance-as-Code Framework
Project ‚Üí ‚ÄúAutomated Compliance-as-Code Framework‚Äù
