üîπ Day 2 ‚Üí Secrets Management in Pipelines
Topics
- Dangers of hardcoding secrets in CI/CD.
- Tools: Vault, SOPS, GitHub Actions Secrets, Sealed Secrets.
- Best practices ‚Üí rotate, encrypt, restrict access.
Practice
- Integrate HashiCorp Vault with GitHub Actions ‚Üí fetch secret at runtime.
- Encrypt K8s secret with SOPS + commit safely.
- Deploy with sealed secrets into Minikube.
Mini-Project
‚û°Ô∏è cicd-secrets-lab/ ‚Üí Repo with Vault + SOPS + sealed secrets workflow.
