- How do you secure secrets in pipelines?
- What‚Äôs the difference between Vault and Sealed Secrets?

üîπ Day 3 ‚Üí Code & Dependency Scanning
Topics
- Code scanning (SAST) with SonarQube / CodeQL.
- Dependency scanning ‚Üí Grype, Dependabot, Snyk.
- CI/CD integration.
Practice
- Add SonarQube scan in GitHub Actions.
- Run Grype on app Docker image.
- Enable Dependabot for repo.
Mini-Project
‚û°Ô∏è cicd-code-scan/ ‚Üí Pipeline with SAST + dependency scan.
Interview Qs
- What‚Äôs the difference between SAST and Dependency Scanning?
- How do you enforce ‚Äúfail on critical CVEs‚Äù?

üîπ Day 4 ‚Üí Dynamic & IaC Scanning
Topics
- DAST (Dynamic App Security Testing) ‚Üí ZAP, Nikto.
- IaC scanning (Terraform, Helm, K8s manifests).
- Tools: Checkov, Terrascan, KubeLinter.
Practice
- Add OWASP ZAP DAST scan in pipeline (test app endpoint).
- Run Checkov on Terraform code ‚Üí fail on public S3.
- Run KubeLinter on K8s manifests.
Mini-Project
‚û°Ô∏è cicd-iac-dast-lab/ ‚Üí Repo with DAST + IaC scanning workflows.
