- Extra tool exposure (Gremlin, BloodHound, Shuffle SOAR, Fugue/Wiz).
üëâ With this, your roadmap shifts from just hands-on labs ‚Üí to real-world failure handling, detection tuning, and multi-cloud security strategy.

Week 49, you‚Äôre already at a DevSecOps + Cloud Security Engineer hybrid level: Chaos Engineering, Red/Purple Teaming, Multi-Cloud Security, GitOps Security, IR/Forensics.
Now it‚Äôs time to focus on Supply Chain Security & Software Integrity ‚Äî one of the hottest areas in DevSecOps today (post-SolarWinds, Log4Shell, dependency attacks). This will make you interview-proof for 2025+ cloud-native security trends.

üìÖ Week 49: Supply Chain Security (SLSA, SBOM, Sigstore)
üéØ Goal
- Understand supply chain attack vectors (dependency hijacking, CI/CD poisoning, image tampering).
- Learn SBOM (Software Bill of Materials) and SLSA framework.
- Secure build ‚Üí sign artifacts ‚Üí verify in pipelines.
- Deliver a Supply Chain Security Lab repo.

üîπ Day 1 ‚Üí Supply Chain Security Fundamentals
Topics
- Supply chain attack case studies ‚Üí SolarWinds, Log4Shell, CodeCov breach.
- Threat areas: dependencies, build systems, images, registries.
- Standards: SLSA (Supply-chain Levels for Software Artifacts).
Practice
- Draw attack surface for a CI/CD pipeline (developer ‚Üí repo ‚Üí build ‚Üí deploy).
- Identify weak spots in your own Secure CI/CD Framework (Week 43).
Mini-Project
‚û°Ô∏è supplychain-basics/ ‚Üí Attack surface diagram + notes on risks.
Interview Qs
- What is SLSA and why is it important?
- How do supply chain attacks differ from runtime attacks?

üîπ Day 2 ‚Üí SBOM (Software Bill of Materials)
Topics
- What is SBOM? Why it‚Äôs critical for vulnerability tracking.
- Tools: Syft, CycloneDX, SPDX.
- Use cases: compliance, vulnerability alerts, audits.
Practice
- Generate SBOM for your app Docker image with Syft.
- Export SBOM in CycloneDX format.
- Upload SBOM to GitHub Security Dashboard.
Mini-Project
‚û°Ô∏è sbom-lab/ ‚Üí SBOM reports for multiple apps/images.
Interview Qs
- What‚Äôs the purpose of SBOM in DevSecOps?
- Which formats are common and why?

üîπ Day 3 ‚Üí Image & Dependency Scanning at Depth
Topics
- Dependency confusion & typosquatting (npm, PyPI).
- Deep image scanning: Trivy, Grype.
- Integrating SBOM + scanning.
Practice
- Run Grype against SBOM generated by Syft.
- Detect vulnerabilities across dependencies.
- Simulate dependency hijack (local PyPI server).
Mini-Project
‚û°Ô∏è supplychain-scanning/ ‚Üí Repo with SBOM + scan reports + dependency test.
