- How do you detect dependency confusion?
- What‚Äôs the difference between SCA and SBOM?

üîπ Day 4 ‚Üí Signing & Verifying Artifacts (Sigstore)
Topics
- Why signing matters: preventing tampering.
- Sigstore ‚Üí Cosign, Fulcio, Rekor.
- Signed artifacts in CI/CD & GitOps.
Practice
- Sign a Docker image with Cosign.
- Store signature in Rekor transparency log.
- Verify image signature in pipeline.
Mini-Project
‚û°Ô∏è sigstore-lab/ ‚Üí Signed Docker image + verification demo.
