- How does Cosign ensure image integrity?
- Why is transparency log important?

üîπ Day 5 ‚Üí Secure Registries & Build Systems
Topics
- Securing registries ‚Üí Harbor, Amazon ECR, GCP Artifact Registry.
- Build system security ‚Üí hardening Jenkins, GitHub Actions, GitLab CI.
- Preventing poisoned builds.
Practice
- Deploy Harbor registry with Notary v2 (image signing).
- Harden GitHub Actions ‚Üí pin actions by SHA, least privilege tokens.
- Demonstrate attack ‚Üí malicious action injection ‚Üí block via policy.
Mini-Project
‚û°Ô∏è secure-registry-lab/ ‚Üí Hardened registry + CI/CD build configs.
Interview Qs
- How do you secure CI/CD runners?
- Why pin actions instead of version tags?

