Project ‚Üí ‚ÄúEnd-to-End Supply Chain Security Lab‚Äù
Features:
- SBOM (Syft, CycloneDX).
- Scanning (Grype, Trivy).
- Signing (Cosign, Harbor).
- Verification in GitHub Actions.
- Policy ‚Üí only signed + scanned artifacts allowed.
Deliverables
